text: Mara Keggi (born October 7, 1962) is an American rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. She is the daughter of Latvian orthopedic surgeon Kristaps Keggi. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
